<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL39">
<l>aṭimaiyil kuṭimai yillā ayalcatup pēti māriṟ</l>
<l>kuṭimaiyil kaṭaimai paṭṭa kukkariṟ piṟappa rēlum</l>
<l>muṭiyiṉiṟ ṟuḷapam vaittāy moykaḻaṟ kaṉpu ceyyu</l>
<l>maṭiyarai yukatti pōlu maraṅkamā nakaru ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who have placed tulasī on [Your] head!</l>
<l>You seem to delight in the devotees who love Your feet swarmed [by bees],</l>
<l rend="indent">---even if they are born among contemptible people of</l>
<l rend="indent">dog[-like low births] among the meanest of lineages---</l>
<l rend="indent">more than in Brahmins well-versed in the four Vedas</l>
<l rend="indent">alien to serving [You],</l>
<l rend="indent">devoid of a [good] lineage [when it comes] to serving [You]</l>
<l>O You from the big city of Raṅgam!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
